description:
TV Food Maps is not is neither affiliated with nor endorsed by any networks or shows referenced below.

Want to eat like Guy Fieri host of Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives?

TVFoodMaps allows you to find, track and hopefully eat at the restaurants you see on your favorite Food Network and Travel shows like Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Man v. Food, Best Thing I Ever Ate, No Reservations, Top Chef and more.  With more than 35 shows and over 4000 restaurants TVFoodMaps is the most comprehensive list of restaurants seen on TV you can find in a single app.   We provide features like restaurants nearby, search, road trip planner, custom list management as well information about restaurants like menus, hours of operation and comments.

Things You Can Do:
* Find Restaurants Nearby
* Find Restaurants for your next trip
* Plan a Road Trip
* Bookmarks Restaurants you want to try
* View Restaurant Menus (where available)
* Connect to travel services like Concur & Trip It!
* More!

Our premium upgrade removes all ads from the application.  We've removed functional restrictions hoping that those who like the app will upgrade to premium to help support continued development and maintenance of the restaurants and shows.

If you have any issues or question with this app please contact us directly at tvfoodmaps@gmail.com - we will work to fix all issues. 

Also, check out out website http://www.tvfoodmaps.com
